 <h2>Pet Zoning Upgrade on Test!</h2><br><br>The ability for pets to cross zonelines has long been something mages and beastlords in particular, but also the rest of the EverQuest community, have wanted.<br><br>The reason for not including such functionality has never been a balance issue or design choice, but a matter of game mechanics being unable to support it. Now, possibly due to feedback at the <b>EverQuest Guild Summit</b>, the upgrades have gone onto test.<br><br>Not only can pets cross zonelines, but they retain all buffs and items! You can even camp out for up to 30 minutes with them, the same as no-rent items. So you won't loose your pet by even going linkdead.<br><br>Obviously, the changes are more than welcome! I for one am <b>very</b> pleased with Sony in recent months.<br><br>Lets hope this is one of many great changes to follow!<br><br><br><br></center><br><b><u>Comments/Feedback:</u></b><br><br><i><b>Lol Right!</b> says:</i><br>"As magicians, this helps us more than any other class"

It helps Necro's the most. All Necromancer pets level 59+ require a bonechip AND a peridot to summon a pet.

So every pet a Necro loses costs them around 10pp.<br><br><i><b>Anonymous</b> says:</i><br>ok, can ya charm a pet and then take IT to a different zone?<br><br><i><b>Bard</b> says:</i><br>That would be wicked if ya could, Charm an IG and drag his but to Oasis. That would looks sooo outta place.<br><br><i><b>Anonymous</b> says:</i><br>Or take that same IG to Pok and let it loose? Hmm, something tells me that will not be allowed.<br><br><i><b>Anonymous</b> says:</i><br>Cannot take charmed pets accross zone because their models are not loaded into every zone.  Only summoned pets will be able to cross zone lines because they are all loaded into every zone at all times.  <br><br><i><b>EQplayer</b> says:</i><br>they're making EQ too easy... soom enough all u have to do it click a couple buttons on your keyboard and the game will be played for you.... not that i dont like this upgrade (cause i REALLY do) but that if they keep making upgrades then people will get bored of having nothing to do...<br><br><i><b>Anonymous</b> says:</i><br>well they will still find something to gripe about<br><br><i><b>Anonymous</b> says:</i><br>great idea... when will this be put on all of the servers? I wanna stop recastiong over and over over over and over........ and over
<br><br><i><b>Jimmerz</b> says:</i><br>I think that this is a great idea.  I would hope that if they found a way to charm an IG that if it came uncharmed that it would just zone back in to the zone it came from.  How would you like it if you got waxed in PoK by named from the plains... i wouldn't... lets keep it fair and still find a way to keep our pets.... huh...!!!! 
